The Super Eagles head coach, Gernot Rohr has listed five teams that are favourites to win the 2018 FIFA World Cup in Russia. He said the clear favourites for football’s greatest showpiece are Germany, Spain, Brazil, Argentina and France. According to him, the teams have a lot of big players and a “lot of winning mentality”. […] The post Super Eagles Coach Names 5 Favourites To Win 2018 World Cup appeared first on The Herald Nigeria Newspaper.   Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook This post was syndicated from The Herald Nigeria Newspaper. Click here to read the full text on the original website.